stories.title: India to appeal Ganguly ban
stories.subTitle: India v Pakistan, 4th ODI, Ahmedabad
stories.summary: Ranbir Singh Mahendra, the president of the Indian board, has said that an appeal is being planned against the six-match ban imposed on Sourav Ganguly after India failed to bowl their overs quickly enough in Tuesday's fourth ODI at Ahmedabad

stories.subTitle: India v Pakistan, 4th ODI, Ahmedabad
